=Episode 8=

16
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,599
That means

17
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,520
none of these six teams

18
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,639
has Si Lili in them.

19
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,039
The real Si Lili

20
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,080
has long lurked

21
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,240
outside of everyone's attention.

22
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,919
So I just don't get it.

23
00:02:23,719 --> 00:02:24,680
It makes sense

24
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,520
if she escapes silently.

25
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,199
Why did she do all that?

26
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:29,919
Because of the tension

27
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:30,719
between Nanqing and Beiqi at the moment.

28
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:31,919
War could break out any time soon.

29
00:02:32,319 --> 00:02:33,759
What's the connection with that?

30
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,840
The security at the north
must be very strict now.

31
00:02:36,319 --> 00:02:37,639
It's not the right time for her to go.

32
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,599
There would be an equally lot of passes

33
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,439
which are equally strict

34
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,280
if she escapes secretly.

35
00:02:42,759 --> 00:02:43,680
After she did all that,

36
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,360
the security at the north

37
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,919
will check more strictly.

38
00:02:50,719 --> 00:02:52,960
So she doesn't necessarily go north.

39
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,280
Doesn't she go back to Beiqi?

40
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:56,960
She does!

41
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:00,960
Wang Qinian,

42
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,759
is there any other way to Beiqi

43
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:04,120
without going north?

44
00:03:06,039 --> 00:03:08,120
The way to Beiqi without going north?!

45
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,759
Isn't that...

46
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:18,919
There is indeed a way.

47
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,240
Go ahead.

48
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,199
Instead of going north,
go east directly.

49
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:24,840
Find the merchant ships
and return to Beiqi by sea.

50
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:26,879
Which port is the most possible?

51
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:29,000
Dongyi Town! Oh no!

52
00:03:31,039 --> 00:03:33,599
We have very strict security
at Dongyi Town.

53
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,319
Besides, there are a lot of passes

54
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,960
on the way to Dongyi Town as well.

55
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,479
Other than that,

56
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:42,479
this would be the most possible place.

57
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,520
Your Excellency,

58
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,879
do you find this place familiar?

59
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,240
With your drawing like this,

60
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,639
how should I find it familiar?
Just say it.

61
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,919
This is the place

62
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:51,840
Your Excellency grow up.

63
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,240
Danzhou harbor.

64
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:55,719
Yes, it is!

65
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,479
It's all within Nanqing

66
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,240
from the capital city to Danzhou harbor.

67
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:02,000
So it should be Danzhou harbor.

68
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,280
Check it out again!

69
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,120
From the north gate of the capital city

70
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,159
to Danzhou harbor,

71
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,280
which route is the most convenient?

72
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:14,560
What's up?

73
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,360
There is a lot of mountain ranges

74
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:21,120
and passes during the way

75
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,639
from the north gate to Danzhou harbor.

76
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,199
That's not an easy route either.

77
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,360
There is a simpler way.

78
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:32,360
Go ahead.

79
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,439
To return to the capital

80
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,199
and depart from the east gate.

81
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,079
You don't need to go back.

82
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,639
Move the carriage
into the woods and burn it.

83
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,720
After that, leave to different directions
and don't leave any mark.

84
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:40,519
Yes!

85
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,399
According to
Your Excellency's reasoning,

86
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,399
Si Lili may be ahead of us

87
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:53,920
for a short distance.

88
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,879
Indeed! Judging from their reaction,

89
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,079
Zhu Ge should find out

90
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:58,439
Si Lili's whereabouts today.

91
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,879
If she is patient enough,

92
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,000
she will wait
for the Investigator's Office

93
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,240
to focus its attention all on the north

94
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,480
before she returns back to go eastwards.

95
00:06:04,399 --> 00:06:07,120
Your Excellency's wisdom
is indeed stunning.

96
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:09,480
I am totally shocked

97
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,399
by your extraordinary talent.

98
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,680
It gives me a constant sense of anxiety.

99
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,000
Excuse me,

100
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,279
feed my horse with premium forage

101
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,360
and give me a premium room.

102
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,560
Sure! This way please.

103
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,879
Gentlemen, do you need accommodation?

104
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:58,720
That's not necessary.

105
00:07:00,519 --> 00:07:00,879
Yes!

106
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,839
Sure! Please come this way!

107
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,600
Your Excellency,
let's have a look inside.

108
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:06,199
Come here.

109
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,319
Sir, come this way!

110
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,920
Get us a good room!

111
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,360
OK.

112
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,680
Sir, that one is taken.

113
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,079
Come this way!

114
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,439
I'm sorry!

115
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:58,839
This room

116
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,040
faces the sun and it's spacious.

117
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,879
It's very cozy!

118
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,480
Your Excellency!

119
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,079
Do we really need the room?

120
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:08,879
Your Excellency, trust me!

121
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,240
After the long journey of hunting,

122
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,519
rest is more important than time.

123
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,160
Please!

124
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:21,959
Please!

125
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,519
Get us some hot water!

126
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,199
Sure! Please wait a moment!

127
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,480
Waiter!

128
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,519
Miss, what can I do for you?

129
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,200
There it comes!

130
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,600
Sir, here comes the food for you.

131
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,399
Close the door!

132
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,360
Enjoy!

133
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:11,639
Your Excellency,

134
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,799
if Si Lili

135
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,320
really goes eastward,

136
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:17,600
we'll surely catch up with her

137
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:19,360
in two to three days.

138
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,080
She should have a horse.

139
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,000
Your Excellency,

140
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:26,039
if there is no backup horse,

141
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:29,159
she won't travel that fast
with just one horse.

142
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:30,360
Just think about it.

143
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,720
The horse needs
to take rests once in a while

144
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,519
when it is running.

145
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,519
And it has to be fed

146
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:37,279
with premium forage from time to time,

147
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:38,240
otherwise it will die

148
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:41,039
of fatigue.

149
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:41,960
The road we take

150
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:44,679
is actually a short cut
between the hills

151
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,879
which is faster than the official road.

152
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:50,600
The shortest way is
the straight line between two points.

153
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:53,360
What did you say?

154
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:54,879
Nothing.

155
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,320
Your Excellency,

156
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:00,840
will you pay

157
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,120
for the room and food?

158
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:03,639
Certainly!

159
00:10:04,279 --> 00:10:05,279
Then it's not that weary!

160
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,559
Let's finish it!

161
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:09,480
Wait!

162
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:12,960
After you, Your Excellency!

163
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,639
It's poisonous!

164
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,159
Is it...

165
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:29,519
It seems we don't need
to wait for two to three days.

166
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:31,320
It is made

167
00:10:31,639 --> 00:10:32,639
by the kitchen.

168
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:33,679
Where did you fetch it
after taken from the kitchen?

169
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,480
I fetched it directly to your room.

170
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,200
Who touched it in between?

171
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,000
No.

172
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,440
Alright!

173
00:10:38,879 --> 00:10:40,120
Then you're solely liable.

174
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:40,679
Follow me.

175
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,799
Look at him!

176
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:43,440
Look at him with your own eyes!

177
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,240
Don't you leave!

178
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,960
There is poison in the food
and someone died with it.

179
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,120
What do we do now?
I'll notify the imperial court!

180
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:57,919
Nah.

181
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:58,440
Eh...

182
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,720
How could it happen?

183
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,559
I'm afraid you're the murder

184
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:01,480
in this case.

185
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,240
No! No! No!

186
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,320
It's not me! It's not me!

187
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,240
Didn't you say

188
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,360
only the kitchen
and you touched the food?

189
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,279
Or this inn

190
00:11:06,279 --> 00:11:06,840
is a sinister inn?

191
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:08,159
No! No!

192
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,799
A lady touched it!

193
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,159
Who is the lady?

194
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,600
She checked in this afternoon as well!

195
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:15,679
She insisted on

196
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:17,039
checking out
the quality of the food here

197
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,000
before she decided
whether to eat here or not.

198
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,799
So I brought your food box to her

199
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:21,720
to have a look.

200
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,159
I did nothing else.

201
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,919
Why did you pick ours in particular?

202
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,919
Because you live close!

203
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:27,919
Just the opposite side.

204
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:35,000
He is alive again!

205
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:54,200
Your Excellency,

206
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:56,039
there is no trace left at all.

207
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:57,600
I just asked the waiter.

208
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,480
The lady has gone.

209
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,080
Is she Si Lili?

210
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,039
Not sure!

211
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:27,639
It is she without doubt.

212
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,159
What's your source of judgement?

213
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:31,039
The smell of the Chenguang.

214
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:32,679
What is that?

215
00:12:34,639 --> 00:12:35,759
A type of incense

216
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:38,559
that has been used
by the Joy Tsin House all the time.

217
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:40,399
Its smell is enduring

218
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,759
and doesn't fade easily. Have a try!

219
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,639
How do you know that?

220
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,679
tracking.

221
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,440
to make judgement
according to the fragrance.

222
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,519
That's the basic of hunting.

223
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,679
I mean how do you know

224
00:13:01,679 --> 00:13:03,440
what type of incense
the Joy Tsin House uses.

225
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:07,600
Honestly,

226
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,080
I have also been

227
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,039
to the Joy Tsin House.

228
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,200
But only to enjoy the singing.

229
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,320
Nothing else.

230
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,480
Are you able to hold it?

231
00:13:20,759 --> 00:13:21,960
It's just too expensive there.

232
00:13:22,279 --> 00:13:24,000
I can't afford it,

233
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,720
nor do I have the guts.

234
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:27,879
Your Excellency! Your Excellency!

235
00:13:27,919 --> 00:13:28,840
it must be held back

236
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,799
from my wife,

237
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:31,000
or my life will be...

238
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,039
Enough of that.

239
00:13:33,639 --> 00:13:35,000
Since the incense smell is confirmed,

240
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,120
it should be Si Lili.

241
00:13:37,519 --> 00:13:39,399
Let's hunt her down tonight.

242
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,960
Maybe, we'll get something.

243
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:43,120
Clean your face immediately.

244
00:13:43,159 --> 00:13:43,600
We're doing it now.

245
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,639
That lady rode her own horse

246
00:13:49,799 --> 00:13:50,720
towards the Pijia Hill.

247
00:13:51,679 --> 00:13:52,559
There are two ways

248
00:13:52,679 --> 00:13:53,720
to the Danzhou Harbor.

249
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,960
One is the Pijia Hill.

250
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,200
Second is the Chaomeng River.

251
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:58,960
How do you know where she went?

252
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,559
She inquired about the way.

253
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:02,360
I persuaded her
not to travel in the evening

254
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:03,559
as the Pijia Hill

255
00:14:03,759 --> 00:14:04,480
is swarmed with robbers,

256
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,200
but she just didn't listen.

257
00:14:07,519 --> 00:14:07,960
Thank you.

258
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,000
Let's go.

259
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,559
Sure!

260
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:12,759
Hold on.

261
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:21,320
Soybean, alfalfa, and eggs.

262
00:14:22,399 --> 00:14:22,919
Your Excellency,

263
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,559
what her horse took

264
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:25,960
was premium forage.

265
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,559
It is all plains and hills

266
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:29,320
in the Pijia Hill region.

267
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,519
That's very convenient
for horses to travel.

268
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,799
If we are to catch up with her,

269
00:14:33,039 --> 00:14:34,440
we'd better take horses as well.

270
00:15:08,919 --> 00:15:09,360
What's up?

271
00:15:11,919 --> 00:15:13,159
There is fresh horse waste there.

272
00:15:41,399 --> 00:15:42,879
Well, Your Excellency,

273
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:45,559
this is the premium forage from the inn.

274
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:47,080
We're on the right track.

275
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,039
Si Lili should be ahead of us.

276
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:55,000
Wait a minute!

277
00:15:56,919 --> 00:15:57,399
What's up, Your Excellency?

278
00:15:58,279 --> 00:15:59,000
It makes me feel so awkward

279
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,360
when I saw you

280
00:16:00,519 --> 00:16:01,759
eating it just now.

281
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:02,480
Your Excellency,

282
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:04,960
I didn't eat it.

283
00:16:05,120 --> 00:16:06,200
Don't you think it's too smooth?

284
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,440
What is too smooth?

285
