a live Beiqi agent.

569
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,720
Once they get

570
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:39,759
any new intelligence from you,

571
00:29:39,839 --> 00:29:41,440
it will be a great achievement.

572
00:29:49,759 --> 00:29:50,880
You know it very well that

573
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:53,240
no matter to which side I hand you over,

574
00:29:54,119 --> 00:29:54,799
what awaits you ahead

575
00:29:54,799 --> 00:29:56,359
is endless excruciation.

576
00:29:56,759 --> 00:29:57,599
Dying will be luxurious

577
00:29:57,599 --> 00:29:59,039
by then.

578
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:07,480
Your heartbeat is faster.
Are you nervous?

579
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:12,839
Who is the head of conspiracy
for the Niulan Street assassination?

580
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:20,200
Why does it have to have a head?

581
00:30:21,799 --> 00:30:22,839
Why can't I be the person

582
00:30:22,839 --> 00:30:23,960
to have planned it all?

583
00:30:24,519 --> 00:30:25,599
You don't have the motive to kill me.

584
00:30:28,359 --> 00:30:29,319
Is it the fairyland

585
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,319
I'm so deeply into you,

586
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,759
Mr. Fan?

587
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:39,440
You're a Beiqi agent

588
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:42,680
who's been lurking in the capital city
for so many years.

589
00:30:44,359 --> 00:30:45,400
No one knows

590
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,599
how much efforts you've made

591
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,359
to become the courtesan
in the Joy Tsin House.

592
00:30:50,319 --> 00:30:52,480
The people you're in touch with
are all high officials and celebrities.

593
00:30:52,559 --> 00:30:53,960
It's the prime time

594
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:55,000
to collect intelligence.

595
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,880
Your exposure of identity now

596
00:30:59,480 --> 00:31:01,160
will ruin all your previous efforts.

597
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:05,200
It'll make sense

598
00:31:05,799 --> 00:31:07,759
if it's the Crown Prince, His Majesty,

599
00:31:07,759 --> 00:31:08,680
or the Prime Minister
that you're trying to kill

600
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,079
after all these efforts.

601
00:31:12,759 --> 00:31:13,720
It is otherwise

602
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,400
if your target is me.

603
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,839
What fantastic reasoning!

604
00:31:21,559 --> 00:31:22,839
Is that a confirmation

605
00:31:23,519 --> 00:31:25,119
that someone else is behind it?

606
00:31:26,559 --> 00:31:27,640
Why don't you figure it out yourself

607
00:31:28,759 --> 00:31:29,640
since you're so smart?

608
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,680
Who is it?

609
00:31:31,079 --> 00:31:32,759
Why don't you just tell me

610
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,480
and I'll save your life?

611
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:47,720
As you said

612
00:31:48,359 --> 00:31:49,640
just now,

613
00:31:50,519 --> 00:31:51,960
every ministry wants to interrogate me.

614
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:54,200
How do you save me from that?

615
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,240
You'll hand me over anyway

616
00:31:58,039 --> 00:31:59,720
after we arrive
at the capital city tomorrow.

617
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:02,480
It makes no difference

618
00:32:03,119 --> 00:32:04,000
to say it or not to say it.

619
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,400
You're the prisoner
of the Investigator's Office.

620
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,160
I don't need to hand you over.

621
00:32:12,759 --> 00:32:14,440
Should you be really important

622
00:32:14,519 --> 00:32:15,559
in the Investigator's Office,

623
00:32:16,039 --> 00:32:17,200
how come you chase me

624
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:17,920
without any retinues?

625
00:32:19,319 --> 00:32:20,799
That's non-sense. I am his retinue.

626
00:32:24,319 --> 00:32:25,440
Have some water please, Your Excellency!

627
00:32:31,039 --> 00:32:33,039
Keeping it a secret,

628
00:32:34,160 --> 00:32:36,400
I may still get rescued by that person.

629
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:38,559
If I really speak it out,

630
00:32:39,759 --> 00:32:41,480
I'll end up on the chopping block.

631
00:32:42,599 --> 00:32:43,920
Saving you now is too difficult.

632
00:32:44,079 --> 00:32:45,559
I would kill you to keep
your mouth shut if I were that big figure.

633
00:32:46,839 --> 00:32:47,720
As you said yourself,

634
00:32:48,519 --> 00:32:49,319
what awaits me ahead

635
00:32:49,319 --> 00:32:50,640
is endless excruciation.

636
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:53,160
Getting killed

637
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,720
is no less of an extrication.

638
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:07,319
How about

639
00:33:07,359 --> 00:33:08,880
you telling me the name secretly

640
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,000
and then I set you free secretly?

641
00:33:15,839 --> 00:33:17,119
Are you serious?

642
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:20,319
Right now,

643
00:33:20,559 --> 00:33:22,319
the eyes of every ministry
are cast on me.

644
00:33:23,519 --> 00:33:24,519
You dare to set me free now?

645
00:34:01,279 --> 00:34:01,759
Your Excellency,

646
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:04,559
we'd better go back to watch over her.

647
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:05,079
No need.

648
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:06,440
I'm afraid this yard

649
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:07,799
should have been encircled

650
00:34:07,799 --> 00:34:08,320
by all the scouts
from different ministries.

651
00:34:09,119 --> 00:34:09,760
She can't escape.

652
00:34:22,039 --> 00:34:23,440
If we had known that earlier,

653
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,639
we could have taken our time

654
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,880
for the return trip.

655
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,480
Black knights' showing up

656
00:34:31,639 --> 00:34:32,519
means the Head

657
00:34:32,519 --> 00:34:33,559
already knows about it.

658
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,519
If we don't return immediately,

659
00:34:35,519 --> 00:34:36,559
it's very suspicious
that we're colluding with the enemies.

660
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:38,519
That's dangerous to the family.

661
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:41,039
You're right, Your Excellency.

662
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,599
But Master Shadow said

663
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,920
you can do whatever you think necessary

664
00:34:47,199 --> 00:34:48,159
and the Head will help you

665
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:49,760
if anything goes wrong.

666
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:52,480
Chen Pingping and I
are neither families nor friends.

667
00:34:53,039 --> 00:34:54,000
Why would he help me?

668
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:57,719
Your Excellency still don't trust him.

669
00:35:01,719 --> 00:35:02,719
Human mind is changeable.

670
00:35:03,119 --> 00:35:04,400
I can't trust him

671
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:05,960
before I meet him in person.

672
00:35:09,719 --> 00:35:10,119
Your Excellency,

673
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,320
before handing over Si Lili,

674
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,079
you still have another option.

675
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,800
Do you mean to lynch?

676
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:25,039
Yeah!

677
00:35:25,119 --> 00:35:26,079
Now Si Lili

678
00:35:26,079 --> 00:35:27,320
is under your control.

679
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,800
If you lynch her,

680
00:35:30,440 --> 00:35:31,400
she probably will tell the truth

681
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:34,440
after one night's of torture.

682
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,119
It's very easy

683
00:35:39,119 --> 00:35:39,679
to torture a weak lady.

684
00:35:40,719 --> 00:35:41,920
But if we have no bottom-line,

685
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:43,440
are we any different from animals?

686
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:47,920
You're right, Your Excellency.

687
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:49,639
So,

688
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:51,519
we'll have to wait

689
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:52,480
before making a decision?

690
00:35:52,519 --> 00:35:54,159
after we get back to the capital city.

691
00:35:56,679 --> 00:35:57,320
Wang Qinian,

692
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,519
If I chose to lynch

693
00:35:59,519 --> 00:36:00,440
just now,

694
00:36:01,159 --> 00:36:02,519
will you leave me?

695
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:06,519
If Your Excellency has no bottom-line,

696
00:36:07,519 --> 00:36:08,480
then my monthly payment

697
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:09,679
of 150 taels of silvers

698
00:36:09,679 --> 00:36:10,679
will not be guaranteed.

699
00:36:11,559 --> 00:36:12,840
50 taels! 50 taels!

700
00:36:14,239 --> 00:36:15,000
Your Excellency, do feel relieved.

701
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:17,800
As long as you keep paying me
50 taels of silver,

702
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:19,440
Wang Qinian,

703
00:36:19,719 --> 00:36:22,280
and serve you.

704
00:36:36,119 --> 00:36:37,079
They are all

705
00:36:37,079 --> 00:36:38,199
so eager!

706
00:36:39,519 --> 00:36:40,440
It is a big case after all.

707
00:36:41,239 --> 00:36:42,320
If you don't have the support

708
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:43,400
from the Investigator's Office,

709
00:36:43,719 --> 00:36:45,360
we may not be able to hold her.

710
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:12,960
Si Lili is the prisoner
of the Investigator's Office.

711
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:14,840
Your Excellencies,

712
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:17,760
please make way for us!

713
00:37:18,079 --> 00:37:18,760
Mr. Fan,

714
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:20,960
we have no objection

715
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:21,719
if the Investigator's Office

716
00:37:22,159 --> 00:37:23,159
really wants the prisoner.

717
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:25,119
Please show us the arrest warrant

718
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:27,280
of the Investigator's Office.

719
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:32,639
We'll make it up later on.

720
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,559
I'm afraid that's a breach of the rule.

721
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,199
Here comes the arrest warrant!

722
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:07,320
The Investigator's Office
is directly affiliated with His Majesty.

723
00:38:07,719 --> 00:38:09,920
It has the right
to fetch anyone for interrogation

724
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,519
for all matters in
and out of the capital city.

725
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,199
Here is the arrest warrant!

726
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:15,239
If you don't have His Majesty's
sacred edict,

727
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:18,400
I'll take her away.

728
00:38:20,679 --> 00:38:21,159
Follow me!

729
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,079
Why are you still following me?

730
00:38:54,639 --> 00:38:55,159
Your Excellency.

731
00:38:55,719 --> 00:38:56,679
Si Lili's case

732
00:38:57,119 --> 00:38:58,320
is connected with
the Niulan Street assassination.

733
00:38:58,599 --> 00:38:59,440
Can I take charge of the trial?

734
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:01,360
Do you think I'll hand her over to you

735
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:03,039
now that I've come in person?

736
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:06,360
Your Excellency.

737
00:39:06,639 --> 00:39:09,079
Agents and military organizations
are in the domain of the Fourth Division.

738
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,079
You're off the case.

739
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:11,159
She was captured by me.

740
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:12,239
You have all the credit to the capture.

741
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,440
The assassination
is after all related to me.

742
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:15,519
Then you surely need
to stay out to avoid suspicion.

743
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:17,559
Go back!

744
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:31,519
Mr. Fan, aren't you gonna save me?

745
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:32,840
Where are your actions?

746
00:39:44,159 --> 00:39:44,719
Your Excellency!

747
00:39:46,639 --> 00:39:47,239
Your Excellency!

748
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:50,559
Your Excellency!

749
00:39:58,119 --> 00:39:58,719
She is gone!

750
00:39:58,719 --> 00:39:59,800
What's the point of keeping that?

751
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:01,760
Dismantle it and get it disposed!

752
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:20,360
Don't be mad, Your Excellency!

753
00:40:21,559 --> 00:40:23,000
After all, Yan Bingyun, his son,

754
00:40:23,039 --> 00:40:24,039
went to Beiqi

755
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,800
because of you.

756
00:40:26,079 --> 00:40:27,880
Naturally, he's a bit apathetic to you

757
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:29,480
which makes sense.

758
00:40:29,679 --> 00:40:30,239
Are you hungry?

759
00:40:30,719 --> 00:40:31,400
What did you say?

760
00:40:32,119 --> 00:40:33,320
We've been rushing for so many days.

761
00:40:34,119 --> 00:40:35,159
Shall I treat you with a good meal?

762
00:40:36,199 --> 00:40:37,400
No, that's not needed.

763
00:40:38,119 --> 00:40:38,880
Well,

764
00:40:39,199 --> 00:40:40,119
go home

765
00:40:40,239 --> 00:40:41,840
and let my wife know
I'm back safe and sound.

766
00:40:42,039 --> 00:40:43,880
And, I miss my daughter now.

767
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:45,079
Right.

768
00:40:45,519 --> 00:40:46,599
Come to me after you're done!

769
00:40:47,119 --> 00:40:48,119
As you're in my team,

770
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,639
we need to report
to the mansion together.

771
00:40:51,199 --> 00:40:51,840
Got it.

772
00:40:52,719 --> 00:40:55,440
So, you're alright?

773
00:40:55,719 --> 00:40:56,920
Of course!

774
00:40:57,719 --> 00:40:58,519
Remember to come to my mansion.

775
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:11,599
My Lady!

776
00:41:12,599 --> 00:41:13,280
-My Lady! -What happened?

777
00:41:17,719 --> 00:41:18,760
Well, he...

778
00:41:19,760 --> 00:41:20,280
Calm down!

779
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:22,760
Isn't he the miracle-working doctor?

780
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:24,800
He is the miracle-working doctor
and also Fan Xian.

781
00:41:25,199 --> 00:41:26,119
I need to talk to him.

782
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:27,920
Leave us and close the door!

783
00:41:29,039 --> 00:41:29,480
Leave!

784
00:41:42,679 --> 00:41:43,920
Why do you come in day time?

785
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:46,119
I just got back and I want to meet you.

786
00:41:48,519 --> 00:41:50,000
It's said you captured Si Lili.

787
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:51,000
Are you hurt?

788
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:53,079
Safe and sound!

789
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:55,800
I can't get hurt

790
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:56,760
with my proficiency at martial art.

791
00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:58,000
Where is she?

792
00:42:02,519 --> 00:42:03,440
As soon as I went through the gate,

793
00:42:03,679 --> 00:42:04,800
both the Ministry of Personnel and the Ministry
of Penalty came to take her over.

794
00:42:05,159 --> 00:42:06,239
She was eventually taken away
by the Investigator's Office.

795
00:42:07,079 --> 00:42:08,199
Alright! Let's not talk about these.

796
00:42:09,119 --> 00:42:09,920
Is that edible?

797
00:42:10,239 --> 00:42:10,880
I feel hungry now.

798
00:42:13,559 --> 00:42:15,079
That's my leftover.

799
00:42:15,119 --> 00:42:15,840
I don't mind!

800
00:42:31,719 --> 00:42:33,159
You won't give up like this.

801
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:36,800
You can't let go of Teng Zijing's death.

802
00:42:37,239 --> 00:42:37,960
Don't talk!

803
00:42:39,519 --> 00:42:40,320
I just want to sit beside you quietly

804
00:42:41,159 --> 00:42:42,679
like this for a while.

805
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:08,360
I always wondered

806
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:11,320
if I hadn't gone
to the Qing Temple that day,

807
00:43:14,400 --> 00:43:15,079
I would not have met you

808
00:43:15,079 --> 00:43:16,039
holding a drumstick.

809
00:43:18,039 --> 00:43:20,880
Time flows like a river.
Lives are like fishes in it.

810
00:43:21,519 --> 00:43:23,199
They meet in undercurrent
and rapid torrent.

811
00:43:23,519 --> 00:43:24,719
We're destined to meet.

812
00:43:25,559 --> 00:43:26,800
Even if we hadn't met on that day,

813
00:43:27,719 --> 00:43:28,960
we'd meet elsewhere.

814
00:43:29,840 --> 00:43:30,599
We're destined to meet?

815
00:43:31,480 --> 00:43:32,079
Perhaps,

816
00:43:33,559 --> 00:43:34,440
I feel so much settled

817
00:43:35,960 --> 00:43:37,079
after hearing your words.

818
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:46,159
You can turn to Ye Ling'er!

819
00:43:47,679 --> 00:43:49,400
Ye Ling'er? What do I turn to her for?

820
00:43:50,119 --> 00:43:51,360
She's been to the Joy Tsin House.

821
00:43:52,079 --> 00:43:53,440
Why would she go there?

822
00:43:53,679 --> 00:43:54,400
When she knew

823
00:43:54,400 --> 00:43:55,519
you are Fan Xian on that day,

824
00:43:56,079 --> 00:43:57,159
she insisted in visiting
the Joy Tsin House

825
00:43:57,320 --> 00:43:58,320
to check out if there is anything

826
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,320
between you and Si Lili.

827
00:43:59,840 --> 00:44:00,480
After that,

828
00:44:00,679 --> 00:44:01,239
the news became wide spread

829
00:44:01,239 --> 00:44:02,519
that she fell into the water
and got saved.

830
00:44:03,079 --> 00:44:03,639
She never came to meet me

831
00:44:03,639 --> 00:44:04,760
ever since then.

832
00:44:05,320 --> 00:44:06,440
I think

833
00:44:07,159 --> 00:44:08,519
she could have seen something
on that day.

834
00:44:15,599 --> 00:44:16,679
What a coincidence, Mr. Lin.

835
00:44:16,800 --> 00:44:17,719
I'm diagnosing for her.

836
00:44:21,440 --> 00:44:22,079
Second brother,

837
00:44:22,119 --> 00:44:23,159
why are you mad?

838
00:44:23,159 --> 00:44:24,039
You, a bastard from Danzhou!

839
00:44:24,039 --> 00:44:25,039
How dare you step into my sister's room?

840
00:44:25,800 --> 00:44:26,760
How do you know I'm Fan Xian?

841
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:28,079
I must kill you with my sword today.

842
00:44:31,360 --> 00:44:32,760
Take out your sword then.

843
00:44:44,960 --> 00:44:47,199
Brother, we didn't do anything shameful.

844
00:44:47,559 --> 00:44:48,719
If anyone knows about this,

845
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:50,480
